reviews.review_text:
We have a "winner" This was a good show for many reasons other than the music.  All were glad to be back.  The recording reflects that.  You either like '87 or you don't.  If you do, you will like this show.  
The crux is that this seems to me to be the best source for a show that it is hard to find a good version of.  

3* b/c it could still be better.
